 .
 Do the buttons work?

plugin: manual
name: keys/mute
requires: device.product in ['Notebook','Laptop','Portable']
_description:
 Press the mute key on the keyboard. A status window should appear \
 and the volume should mute/unmute when pressed multiple times.
 .
